Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:33.41,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Aimerais-tu, en ce monde, voir quelque chose, s'effacer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:40.24,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Et que l'air soit plus pur, le coeur des hommes transformées
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:47.26,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Et pourtant tout est si fragile ici, sur la terre
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:53.54,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Il n'y a rien qui soit futile, tu sait
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:11.91,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}D'un cote, beaux ou bon est quelque fois, prodigieux
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:19.28,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Et de l'autre, laid ou pauvres est bien souvent, monstrueux
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:26.35,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Qu'importe ce que ton coeur te dictera, souvient toi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:32.03,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Que la différence naît dans tes yeux
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:40.77,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Chante toutes les couleurs du monde
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:47.90,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Sans manquer une seule note
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:54.06,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Chaque choses à sa place ici
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:15:03.78,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Chaque émoi... forme la symphonie... de notre vie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:16.06,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Savoure l'harmonie du ciel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:22.76,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Vois que tout est essentiel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:28.88,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Il comprend que toi aussi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:36.85,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Tu veut écrire, la mélodie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:58.11,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Voudrait tu, de ce monde, pouvoir revoir l'écriture
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:05.12,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Et choisir ses couleurs pour faire ta propre peinture
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:11.90,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Prendre le bien, le mal et sans trier, accepter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:17.57,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Sans couvrir tes yeux, tout regarder
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:26.08,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Joie et malheur ne font qu'un
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:31.65,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Tout est dans leur destin
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:39.43,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}De chaque rime naît un chagrin
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:46.46,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Dans chaque voix... dans chaque petit bruit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:50.00,French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Vit l'infini
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:33.41,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Would you like to see something, in this world, erase itself
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:40.24,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And that the air be purer, the hearts of men transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:47.26,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And yet everything is so fragile here, on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:53.54,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}There is nothing that is futile, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:11.91,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}From one side, beautiful or good is sometimes, prodigious
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:19.28,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And from the other, ugly or poor is often, monstrous
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:26.35,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Whatever your heart dictates to you, remember
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:32.03,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}That the difference is born in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:40.77,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Sing all the colours of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:47.90,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Without missing a single note
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:54.06,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Everything has its place here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:15:03.78,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Every excitement... forms the symphony... of our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:16.06,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Savour the harmony of the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:22.76,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}See that everything is essential
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:28.88,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}He understands that you too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:36.85,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}You want to write, the melody
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:58.11,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Would you like to be able to see the writing of this world again
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:05.12,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And choose the colours to make your own painting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:11.90,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Take the good with the bad, and accept it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:17.57,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't cover your eyes, look at everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:26.08,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Joy and misfortune are one
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:31.65,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Everything is in their destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:39.43,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}In every rhyme a sadness is born
