Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.84,0:00:06.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of Roman troops in no-man's land at Seize's border!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:26.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:36.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We caught the Roman soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:38.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:41.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:47.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we'll join forces with the first and third divisions, which are deployed at the border!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:49.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:49.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:52.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you move, I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:53.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:56.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:00:59.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell your people to get out of the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:03.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(640,681.25)}Music in the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:06.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:07.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:11.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls of the fortress are holding our commander hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:13.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:18.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, it didn't hit any internal organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:19.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:22.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she's in any immediate danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:23.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yumina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:27.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:31.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll become a sacrifice in order to start the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's dead, she won't be valuable anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:43.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past month, we've had Roman troops moving near the borders of our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:48.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid it's a show of force in order to put pressure on the peace talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They have despised us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:55.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Taiko, his majesty, is so weak-kneed that he said to do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:02:00.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order for them to make the first move, we must take a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:06.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, having the prisoner cry and shot dead in front of their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:07.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you guys are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace making is just acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:11.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rome must be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kannagi Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:19.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Our friend, the Witch of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:22.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever think that I wouldn't find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:23.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:26.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël was only used by you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:28.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:32.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that Invisible God of Death has something to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Invisible God of Death!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:38.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're called the genius that comes out once every one-hundred years at the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:40.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Invisible God of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:43.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that restored the biological warfare plant from the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that girl right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:49.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:00.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Put that man in the underground distillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:09.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our colleagues are already in position to battle the Roman military.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:12.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A small incentive can change the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:19.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will we still retreat from the battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was finally over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so unlucky, both of the sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've locked the Colonel up in the distillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:29.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, please eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These are some pastries that I got from Treize. They're delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san, I didn't know that you were still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it got really bad, I would've left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's really messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of Flame would protect the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:01.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotten the town into a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:03.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:10.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Aisha-san about the tale of the Maidens of Flame when we were hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:16.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, she said that in Roman literature, a totally different story is told.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:18.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:22.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of Flame protect the lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:50.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK. I'm still not sure if you can do it well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:54.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is... I'm not sure if you can shoot anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:05:01.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can believe it's right, I might be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:05.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I'm also a maiden at the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:09.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like those Maidens of Flame in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:12.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? You believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A fairy tale created randomly by the Romans?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel I can accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of Flame protect the lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be real, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um? What do you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:55.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how good your hearing is, it wouldn't spread to a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A cease-fire signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:03.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:05.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:08.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early to be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It could have been misheard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:15.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's true, we still don't know if the peace talks were successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we must tell Colonel Hopkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:20.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:23.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was bringing some food to the Colonel, and he's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:28.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so great that you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Start attacking in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought that the Colonel would just listen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:42.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was worth a try, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:48.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:51.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colonel... He laughed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:07:00.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He laughed because he saw the God of Death that I revived and many deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He... {\alpha&HFF&}kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:05.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He... kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He fights until there's no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:14.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I helped him. Because of my mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:19.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think so, then please save the lives that haven't been taken yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:26.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A cease-fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:32.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that girl's ears should be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! We'd like to be witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:40.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so careless, forgetful, childish and so uncool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan never lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to start a war that much!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:50.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is war that pushes civilisation and science forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The pride that we once had as human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:02.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Roman military plans to start attacking tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we can't avoid the war any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:10.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san's been arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:25.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:26.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:29.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are fighting against the God of Vingt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:32.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to show him the sound that someone showed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:34.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:37.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you just do whatever you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:45.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone said that the world has already ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:49.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I... love this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love all the people here so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:58.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just... give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:09.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha-san said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:24.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\i1}As a soldier, I have killed people too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\i1}I'm just like you, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:39.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... just like... you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\i1}You have suffered enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:45.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've suffered a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:53.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\i1}So even if no one else forgives you... I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, even if...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:17.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:24.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Aisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:30.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go, then there is no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:46.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:50.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:58.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saying "no" to us all these times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:09.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I... do... not... want a girl of the same age as me to be interrogated either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:12.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Rio-senpai is not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:18.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël... and Kanata... are not reliable either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:23.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I must work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being an irresponsible platoon leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:29.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:36.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:43.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All the gods, please bless the Maidens of Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:54.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The main conversion reactor is increasing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:59.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,FAB, FAC, DMR, ECB are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:02.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Superconductivity is stabilising.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem with the weapon-control system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:09.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The main and secondary artilleries have initialised properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Release all the locks on the joints!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:17.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The self weight-reducing system is working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The coefficient is at about negative five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:24.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Departure preparation completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:28.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we perform like we did during training, there won't be any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:30.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, my people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:33.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire the main artillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:35.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ammunition type: Armor-piercing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Armor-piercing ammunition loaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:46.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aimed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan, give the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:49.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:05.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They are starting to attack!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:11.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:48.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kanata-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:50.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemicaduchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:54.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They can use the past's technology to this extent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:57.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Notify all the tankers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:13:59.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try your best to stop them from escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Start attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:02.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to pass here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No war anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:06.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make trouble for the sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:09.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go anyway, you must beat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:10.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:14.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will you do, God of Vingt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:29.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dissolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Join the troops in the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of Flame protect the lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all depending on you, Kanata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the world became like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:15:01.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God sent angels to punish the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:06.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These angels became wounded, so they rested their wings in a town at the end of the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:16.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Maidens who lived in the town's fortress, at the edge of the world, that saved these angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those whom the Maidens should have destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:27.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the Maidens felt sad for those angels,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:31.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So they borrowed power from the huge spider,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:33.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and hid the angels at the bottom of the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:42.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to stop the bleeding, they took turns holding the angels' heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:49.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And in return, the angels gave them the Golden Horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:55.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in the end, the townspeople discovered the angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They set fire to the bottom of the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:05.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens burned in the fire; the angels lost their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:18.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, the angels' troop was discovered. The town's skies were covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:25.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, the sound of the sky started to be heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The angels were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:39.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Golden Horn, which was sounding for the maidens who gave their own lives to save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:55.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you remember that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are pushing it too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl will probably die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:04.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Prepare to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:08.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do this. We're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:24.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are our own people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:36.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose troop is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:38.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It belongs to Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cease-fire signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:03.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Roman military's signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:06.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:08.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to retreat from here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire the main artillery!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we can't stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:14.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:22.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:13.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the attacking! Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:15.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You, drop your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:35.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been sent by the Grand Duke of the Republic of Helvetia, who ranks second in line of succession.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:41.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fiancée of the rightful Roman Emperor, Rio Kazumiya Arkadia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:47.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With the name of my father, the Grand Duke of Helvetia, and the Roman Emperor, I tell you:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:49.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace has been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:52.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't fight at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:55.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Both sides are to retreat as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the order!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\fry-6\fnTimes New Roman\an1\pos(805,368)\frz2.743}As Emperor of the\NRoman Empire and (as)\NPrince of the Helvetian Republic,\NI(we) hereby declare\Nthat peace has been established\Nbetween these two nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fry-6\frz2.743\fnTimes New Roman\an1\pos(27,422)}On Behalf of the\NGrand Duke of the\NRepublic of Helvetia\Nand the rightful Emperor\Nof the Roman Empire, we\Nhereby declare peace\Nbetween our two countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:01.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you dare to disobey, under the name of both kings...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:05.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The First Division of the Imperial Guard of Helvetia will bring you a crushing defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:06.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:15.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:16.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need to fight any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:51.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl! Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:54.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:25.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally spring now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:31.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what was in the letter from Aisha a few days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:37.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2C5A8&\i1}My wounds are healed, and I'm practicing the trumpet every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:37.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Translate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:41.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I'm practicing the trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.05,0:22:42.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:44.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:50.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We received a letter from Rome, but not from the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:54.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be busy. Senpai is the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:23:03.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the battlefield was surrounded by the Imperial Guard so quickly, that we couldn't say anything to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.72,0:23:05.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the sound of Klaus-san's bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:14.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's there, he's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:17.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting so long, and worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:18.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really will...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:19.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:45.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From today on, I, Second Lieutenant Rio Kazumiya Arkadia, am assigned to be a member of Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.39,0:23:49.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Felicia Heideman, please approve my arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.06,0:23:51.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.48,0:23:54.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, we don't have to use rank to address people, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:24:01.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the Roman Emperor really understands people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:07.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides stopping the war, he said he would accept whatever I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.42,0:24:09.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:15.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.09,0:24:16.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:17.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.47,0:24:21.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Rio.
